title: FAKE NEWS PREDICTION
subtitle: Safeguarding Information Integrity in the Digital Era
description: The Fake News Prediction System is an advanced tool designed to identify and classify misinformation and fake news articles with high accuracy. Leveraging state-of-the-art natural language processing (NLP) techniques and machine learning algorithms, this system analyzes textual content to distinguish between reliable and deceptive news sources.
